3. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The planner uses object models to find available suction cup poses, which may involve computer vision techniques. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The planner involves controlling the robot's motion to manipulate objects, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Although not explicitly mentioned, the planner may involve machine learning techniques for object recognition or grasp planning.
